<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>候補者評価サマリー - <%= candidate.user.fullName %></title>
  <%- getChartScript() %>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', 'メイリオ', sans-serif;
      color: #1f2937;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .page {
      padding: 40px;
      min-height: 297mm;
      page-break-after: always;
    }
    .page:last-child {
      page-break-after: avoid;
    }
    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #059669;
    }
    .header-left h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #065f46;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .header-left .subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .logo {
      max-height: 60px;
      max-width: 200px;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #065f46;
      border-left: 4px solid #059669;
      padding-left: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .candidate-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #065f46 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .candidate-name {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .candidate-position {
      font-size: 18px;
      opacity: 0.95;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .candidate-meta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .meta-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .info-card {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .info-card-value {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #059669;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .info-card-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .rating-display {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .rating-stars {
      color: #f59e0b;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .rating-value {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 12px 16px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    th {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    tr:hover {
      background: #f8fafc;
    }
    .interview-status {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .status-SCHEDULED { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
    .status-COMPLETED { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
    .status-CANCELLED { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
    .status-NO_SHOW { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
    .comment-card {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .comment-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .comment-interviewer {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .comment-date {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .comment-rating {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .comment-rating .star {
      color: #f59e0b;
    }
    .comment-rating .star.empty {
      color: #d1d5db;
    }
    .comment-text {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .comment-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .comment-tag {
      background: #e0e7ff;
      color: #3730a3;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .diagnosis-summary {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .diagnosis-type {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .type-code {
      background: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .type-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .tags-container {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .candidate-tag {
      background: #d1fae5;
      color: #065f46;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .disclaimer {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    .disclaimer-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-left">
        <h1>候補者評価サマリー</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">PeopleBooster ATS レポート</div>
      </div>
      <% if (companyLogo) { %>
        <img src="<%= companyLogo %>" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="candidate-card">
      <div class="candidate-name"><%= candidate.user.fullName %></div>
      <div class="candidate-position"><%= candidate.appliedPosition %></div>
      <div class="candidate-meta">
        <div class="meta-item">
          <span class="status-badge"><%= candidate.statusDisplayName %></span>
        </div>
        <% if (candidate.source) { %>
        <div class="meta-item">応募経路: <%= candidate.source %></div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (candidate.assignedTo) { %>
        <div class="meta-item">担当: <%= candidate.assignedTo %></div>
        <% } %>
        <div class="meta-item">登録日: <%= formatDate(candidate.createdAt) %></div>
      </div>
      <% if (candidate.tags && candidate.tags.length > 0) { %>
      <div class="tags-container" style="margin-top: 16px;">
        <% candidate.tags.forEach(function(tag) { %>
          <span class="candidate-tag" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: white;"><%= tag %></span>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">評価サマリー</h2>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-value"><%= summary.totalInterviews %></div>
          <div class="info-card-label">面接回数</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-value"><%= summary.completedInterviews %></div>
          <div class="info-card-label">完了面接</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-value"><%= summary.totalComments %></div>
          <div class="info-card-label">コメント数</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <% if (summary.averageRating) { %>
          <div class="rating-display" style="justify-content: center;">
            <span class="rating-stars">★</span>
            <span class="rating-value"><%= summary.averageRating.toFixed(1) %></span>
          </div>
          <% } else { %>
          <div class="info-card-value">-</div>
          <% } %>
          <div class="info-card-label">平均評価</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if (diagnosis) { %>
    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">診断結果</h2>
      <div class="diagnosis-summary">
        <div class="diagnosis-type">
          <span class="type-code"><%= diagnosis.typeCode %></span>
          <span class="type-name"><%= diagnosis.typeName %></span>
        </div>
        <% if (diagnosis.featureLabels && Array.isArray(diagnosis.featureLabels)) { %>
        <div class="tags-container">
          <% diagnosis.featureLabels.forEach(function(label) { %>
            <span class="candidate-tag" style="background: #e0e7ff; color: #3730a3;"><%= label %></span>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <% if (interviews.length > 0) { %>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">面接スケジュール</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>日時</th>
            <th>形式</th>
            <th>面接官</th>
            <th>所要時間</th>
            <th>ステータス</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% interviews.forEach(function(interview) { %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= formatDate(interview.scheduledAt, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:mm') %></td>
              <td><%= interview.typeDisplayName %></td>
              <td><%= interview.interviewer %></td>
              <td><%= interview.duration %>分</td>
              <td>
                <span class="interview-status status-<%= interview.status %>">
                  <%= interview.statusDisplayName %>
                </span>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% }); %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% } %>

  <% if (comments.length > 0) { %>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">面接コメント</h2>
      <% comments.forEach(function(comment) { %>
        <div class="comment-card">
          <div class="comment-header">
            <span class="comment-interviewer"><%= comment.interviewer %></span>
            <span class="comment-date"><%= formatDate(comment.interviewDate, 'YYYY/MM/DD') %></span>
          </div>
          <% if (comment.rating) { %>
          <div class="comment-rating">
            <% for (var i = 1; i <= 5; i++) { %>
              <span class="star <%= i <= comment.rating ? '' : 'empty' %>">★</span>
            <% } %>
            <span style="margin-left: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">
              (<%= comment.ratingDisplayName %>)
            </span>
          </div>
          <% } %>
          <div class="comment-text"><%= comment.comment %></div>
          <% if (comment.tags && comment.tags.length > 0) { %>
          <div class="comment-tags">
            <% comment.tags.forEach(function(tag) { %>
              <span class="comment-tag"><%= tag %></span>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>

    <div class="disclaimer">
      <div class="disclaimer-title">ご注意（参考情報）</div>
      <p>本レポートに含まれる診断結果はAIによる分析に基づく参考情報です。採用の最終判断は、面接評価やその他の情報と組み合わせて総合的に行ってください。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>生成日時: <%= formatDate(generatedAt, 'YYYY年MM月DD日 HH:mm') %> | 生成者: <%= generatedBy %></p>
    <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> PeopleBooster. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
